biography:

Wolf Vollprecht is the CTO of QuantStack . QuantStack is  the open source consulting company at the heart of mamba package manager and Jupyter.
Wolf is also a core contributor to the conda-forge distribution, and initiator of the RoboStack distribution of robotics related packages.
